      "id": "PopularPost347314",
      "post_content": "When Weatherlight came out, if you used his ability after you declared him as a blocker, he didn't deal combat damage because there was a rule that prevented combat damage from tapped blocked creatures. The removal of that rule made him slightly better, even if only against creatures with one toughness. (And it did screw [Master of Arms](/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master of Arms)'s ability.)",
      "posted_by": "Mode",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost347314\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">When Weatherlight came out, if you used his ability after you declared him as a blocker, he didn't deal combat damage because there was a rule that prevented combat damage from tapped blocked creatures. The removal of that rule made him slightly better, even if only against creatures with one toughness. (And it did screw <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Master of Arms\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Master of Arms\">Master of Arms</a>'s ability.)</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '347314'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy416\">Mode</span>\r\n                                (10/24/2013 4:46:05 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars